      <img src='/assets/images/thoughts/case-study-2023-the-dawn.jpg' width='1342' height='678' loading='lazy' class='border' alt='white and black minimalist website' />
    </figure>

    These initial colors are set with variable fallbacks. I call this initial state of the site ‚ÄúThe Dawn‚Äù so I set those colors like this:

    ```css
    /* light mode */
